{"word":"G5233 - ὑπερβαίνω - hyperbaínō - hoop-er-bah'-ee-no - Go beyond","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperbaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-bah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go beyond</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மீறு"},{"paragraph":"to step over, go beyond"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; to <i>transcend</i>; that is, (figuratively) to <i>overreach:</i> - go beyond.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3845/3845\">G3845</a>, <a href=\"#/G3847/3847\">G3847</a>, <a href=\"#/G3848/3848\">G3848</a>, <a href=\"#/G5233/5233\">G5233</a>, <a href=\"#/G531/531\">G531</a>"}]}